IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User hskimse1@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show hskim/mutt@google"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail-inbox
Far :gmail-remote:INBOX
Near :gmail-local:INBOX
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-sent
Far ":gmail-remote:[Gmail]/보낸편지함"
Near :gmail-local:Sent
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-drafts
Far ":gmail-remote:[Gmail]/임시보관함"
Near :gmail-local:Drafts
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-trash
Far ":gmail-remote:[Gmail]/휴지통"
Near :gmail-local:Trash
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-all
Far ":gmail-remote:[Gmail]/전체보관함"
Near :gmail-local:Archive
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-trash
Channel gmail-all

IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
User hskim@dilluti0n.com
PassCmd "pass show hskim/fastmail.com | awk '/^app-password-eps:/ {print $2}'"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/fastmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/fastmail/Inbox

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
Near :fastmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
